text:
perezhilton.com / Thursday, 20 July 2017 07:15:54

As you may remember, Blac Chyna played Nicki Minaj's body double in Kanye West's Monster video back in 2010 — and now the ladies have reunited in Miami on the set of Minaj's Rake It Up, which features the lyric, "Just to race with Chyna"!
title: Blac Chyna and Nicki Minaj Reunite and Get Their Motors Running for "Rake It Up" Video Shoot
